        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2019-03-11 15:42:41.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 5:\n\n@N Gordon - first of all thanks for the review. Just wanted to answer to the general comment that there is a lot of duplicated logic. Thats 100% right but what is more interesting - it is intentional. This review is for small bug inside the input tab and this bug seems to be a feature rather than bug cause currently a lot of implementation is missing to provide functionality described in the jira ticket. I didnt want to make another bug inside the properties tab and this task is unexpected huge so this is the reason of not making any bigger extraction of common logic for those two components. Unfortunately if we want to do it, we will need to plan such feature with full tests of both of the tabs.\n\nThis comment seems to be crucial here so wanted to answer ASAP. I will try to answer for rest of them tomorrow.",
        "patchset_number": 5
      },
