        "timestamp": "2019-03-20 12:10:27.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 5: Code-Review-2\n\nAccording to your input I think too we should have it as a user story and no ta defect.\nI'd rather not merge code that is a duplicate, we should stick to best practice when possible. Since it's not a high priority defect I suggest to abandon this change for now, until we have a well defined user story and resources",
